name: Pius Moore
description: Easy going, A great sense of humor, Non smoker, Non drinker, Non drugger, Divorced. I enjoy being myself and seeing other people be themselves too. Not driven by money, and believe that what most important in life are the things that we can take with us when we leave. i love cool songs, i love eating fresh fruits and vegetables and enjoy picking blueberries and strawberries when they’re in season.
